explanation:
Dans `vite.config.js`, on ajoute le plugin et on le configure :
```js
import { VitePWA } from 'vite-plugin-pwa';

export default {
  plugins: [
    VitePWA({
      registerType: 'autoUpdate',
      manifest: {
        name: 'Mon E-commerce',
        short_name: 'Eshop',
        theme_color: '#3B82F6',
        icons: [...]
      },
      workbox: {
        globPatterns: ['**/*.{js,css,html,ico,png,svg}']
      }
    })
  ]
};
```
